ame in EQ on a message board someplace it kinda a hack waiting to happen. Not saying this is what it was, just some comments and some maybes to get you to scratch your head and think.<br>
<br>
Its also become popular to setup EQ websites that need &quot;member access&quot; to get to so called &quot;features&quot;. These sites are nothing but honey pots for hackers to get your email and information about you char( Logins , Server, Char names) Once you have supposedly &quot;signed up&quot; for whatever it is , maps , email message board , auction site. They hack you<br>
<br>
Personally i dont trust any EQ related site as far as security goes. Its far , far to easy to get information these days, then engineer social hacks to get more.<br>
<br>
Never use your eq login and password anyplace but eq thats it simply and sweet. Never use the same email you used to sign up for eq for signing up for anything else on the web also.<br>
Use charactors and numbers in random order for your passwords and usernames. Dont use WORDS!!! dictionary brute force attacks are easy to direct these days and becoming more sophisticated. <br>
<br>
 These are just a few things ,anyone else heard of any other way people are scramming now days??? <br>
